  "id": "a018880a-bcef-5fe9-8ea6-135651b12eb2",
  "slug": "brownies-recipe",
  "name": "Brownies Recipe",
  "recipe_type": "dessert",
  "brief_description": "Brownies make a good dessert and snack. It is rich, moist, and undeniably delicious. One thing that I like most about every brownies recipe is the fact that they\u2019re all easy and quick to prepare. This brownies recipe is simple and straightforward; I added a topping of chopped cashews because I remember enjoying this kind\u2026",
  "cuisine": null,
  "instructions": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "text": "Preheat oven to 350 Fahrenheit."
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "text": "Grease a medium baking pan with cooking spray. set aside."
    },
    {
      "position": 3,
      "text": "In a mixing bowl, combine butter, oil, and eggs. Beat until well blended."
    },
    {
      "position": 4,
      "text": "Stir-in the sugar, flour, cocoa powder, vanilla extract, baking powder, and salt. Mix well."
    },
    {
      "position": 5,
      "text": "Pour the mixture in the greased pan. Bake for 28 minutes. Note: in about 20 minutes of baking, sprinkle the chopped cashews evenly on top and continue to bake until the brownies are done."
    },
    {
      "position": 6,
      "text": "Remove from the oven. Let is cool."
    },
    {
      "position": 7,
      "text": "Serve. share and enjoy!"
    }
  ],
  "servings": 6,
  "cooking_time_minutes": 30,
  "preparation_time_minutes": 10,
